title: ** 5 BED / 2 BATH ** 🤩 119 McKibbin St 🤩
posting_body: ['Please text Lihi @ 3477484234 w/ the address 119 McKibbin if interested :)', 'September 1st move in date', 'Half month broker fee', 'Luxury 5 bedroom with big living room and outdoor private deck in the heart of Williamsburg.', 'Big living room second floor apartment in a new two family building, being on the top floor this apartment is equipped with its own private outdoor deck, what more can a home offer?', 'Located: by the L Train Montrose Stop, the J M Train Lorimer Stop, the G Train Broadway Stop All five bedrooms get amazing sunlight they have big windows and some of them even skylights, – they all fit queen beds plus desk and dresser – at least!', 'Living room is big and has windows on two different angles, so for the most part sunlight wont be a problem :) there is central air and heat, Video intercom System, built in speakers in rooms, and A full kitchen with Dishwasher, Gas stove, Fridge / Freezer, and plenty cabinets Showing by appointments only - Half months broker fee due at signing']
